name: Experiment Or Die #20
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. I love anything with interesting typography or illustration and am always on the look out for old magazines or periodicals, and instead of scanning them I take photos at different angles to create a bit of distortion in the reproduction. You really never know what you'll find in out of print science fiction magazines from the 80's. IG:Nikejerk.
